          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2021-03-24T16:52:49Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text>
            <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Inspector General Access Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill transfers responsibility for investigating certain allegations of misconduct from the Department of Justice (DOJ) Office of Professional Responsibility to the DOJ Office of the Inspector General. Specifically, the bill transfers responsibility for allegations relating to a DOJ attorney's authority to investigate, litigate, or provide legal advice.</p>]]>
          </text>
